OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FAn Australian government inquiry into
OL,7,Frising antisemitism before two gunmen
OL,8,Fkilled 15 people at a Hannukah
OL,9,Fcelebration late last year, has
OL,10,Frecommended authorities prioritise gun
OL,11,Freform.
OL,13,FFather and son Sajid and Naveed Akram
OL,14,Fallegedly opened fire with legally-
OL,15,Fowned guns at the celebration at Bondi
OL,16,FBeach on 14 December last year, in an
OL,17,Fattack authorities say was inspired by
OL,18,Fthe Islamic State group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
