OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777551072
OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FRoyal Commissioner Virginia Bell made
OL,7,F14 recommendations in her first
OL,8,Finterim report on Friday, five of
OL,9,Fwhich were not made public because
OL,10,Fthey were classified as confidential
OL,11,Ffor national security reasons.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Anthony Albanese said
OL,14,Fhis government had agreed to implement
OL,15,Fall of the recommendations relevant to
OL,16,Ffederal authorities.
OL,18,FThe report also noted there had been a
OL,19,Fsharp rise in antisemitic incidents in
OL,20,FAustralia since the war between Israel
OL,21,Fand Hamas began on 7 October 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
