OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777551072
OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FThe United States and Israel's attack
OL,7,Fon Iran in February was "likely to
OL,8,Fhave increased the risk of attacks
OL,9,Fdirected at the Australian Jewish
OL,10,Fcommunity," it said.
OL,12,FThe recommendations by the Royal
OL,13,FCommission on Antisemitism and Social
OL,14,FCohesion included that the federal and
OL,15,Fstate governments prioritise
OL,16,Fimplementing nationally consistent gun
OL,17,Flaws and a gun buyback.
