OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FSajid Akram was shot dead by police at
OL,7,Fthe crime scene. He was a licensed
OL,8,Fshooter who legally owned the guns
OL,9,Fused.
OL,11,FUnder new restrictions proposed by the
OL,12,Ffederal government, the Indian-born
OL,13,FAustralian permanent resident would
OL,14,Fhave been banned from holding a gun
OL,15,Flicense because he was not an
OL,16,FAustralian citizen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
