PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777551072
OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FSajid's son, Naveed Akram, was wounded
OL,7,Fbut survived, and has been charged
OL,8,Fwith committing a terrorist act, 15
OL,9,Fcounts of murder and 40 counts of
OL,10,Fattempted murder. He has entered no
OL,11,Fpleas.
OL,13,FThe government also proposed limiting
OL,14,Fthe number of guns someone can own to
OL,15,Fas few as four and implementing
OL,16,Fperiodic reviews of existing gun
OL,17,Flicenses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
