PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777551072
OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FThe new restrictions would be
OL,7,Faccompanied by a gun buyback scheme to
OL,8,Fcompensate gun owners who must hand in
OL,9,Fweapons. The government has proposed
OL,10,Fsharing the cost of the buyback with
OL,11,Fthe six states and two territories.
OL,12,FBut some states have said they won't
OL,13,Fpay.
OL,15,FAlbanese said he hoped the recommended
OL,16,Fgun reforms were implemented.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777551072
OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,F"I certainly hope that that occurs and
OL,7,Fwould continue to engage
OL,8,Fconstructively with state and
OL,9,Fterritory governments to say that this
OL,10,Fis reform which is necessary,"
OL,11,FAlbanese told reporters.
OL,13,FAlbanese noted that despite concluding
OL,14,Fthat risks to Australian Jews were
OL,15,Frising, the report found that no
OL,16,Furgent changes were required to keep
OL,17,FAustralians safe.
OL,19,F"There has been a rise in
OL,20,Fantisemitism. That is a global
OL,21,Fphenomenon," Albanese said.
