OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,F"That is something that has happened
OL,7,Fright around the world. Governments
OL,8,Fneed to respond to it. We are
OL,9,Fresponding to it," he added.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe report noted that the government
OL,17,Fhad allocated 102 million Australian
OL,18,Fdollars (#53 million) to increase
OL,19,Fsecurity at Jewish sites, including
OL,20,Fsynagogues and schools.
