OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,FThe money is administered by the
OL,7,FExecutive Council of Australian Jewry,
OL,8,Fthe community's peak organisation.
OL,10,FThe council's co-chief executive Alex
OL,11,FRyvchin said the report was an
OL,12,Fimportant part in the process of
OL,13,Fmaking Jewish Australians feel safe
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,16,F"We need to get to a point where
OL,17,FJewish Australians at Hanukkah this
OL,18,Fyear ... feel safe, that we can gather
OL,19,Fagain, that we won't be targeted,"
OL,20,FRyvchin told Australian Broadcasting
OL,21,FCorp.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
