OL,3,CInquiry into Sydney antisemitic attack
OL,4,Cthat left 15 dead recommends gun reform
OL,6,F"It's going to be a long process to
OL,7,Fget us to that point. There's a deep
OL,8,Fsense of trauma in the community and
OL,9,F... a lot of unanswered questions, bit
OL,10,Fthis is an important step in the
OL,11,Fprocess," he added.
OL,13,FPublic hearings in the inquiry begin
OL,14,Fon Monday next week.
